data.description: Great opportunity for a young family. Now reduced, call the agent for details property is still available. Please come see a real mid-century beauty loaded with charm and potential. In addition to 2 bedrooms and 2 bathrooms. It features a 1-car detached garage, just begging to be turned into an amazing accessory dwelling. There is also enough rear yard for another unit, for your family entertaining and / or enough room for children to play in there swing sets. Did I say that the long driveway also offers potential for RV access. There is copper plumbing,  central heating and AC and so much more, This home has been well maintained and it shows it. Thanks for your consideration.
